Title: KitchenAid Artisan — The Icon
Author: wavelet-director

INT. WARM KITCHEN - MORNING

Cracked egg falls in slow motion into a polished stainless mixing bowl. Yolk shines. A single drop of milk lands beside it.

CUT TO:

INT. WARM KITCHEN - MORNING

A baker's hands tilt the head of an Empire Red KitchenAid Artisan stand mixer down into position. The chrome bowl-clamp clicks.

CUT TO:

INT. WARM KITCHEN - MORNING

Macro on the spiral dough hook spinning slowly. Pale dough catches the hook, folds over itself, takes shape.

CUT TO:

INT. WARM KITCHEN - MORNING

Slow push-in on the stainless bowl. Flour-dusted dough swirls inside as the Empire Red body looms behind.

CUT TO:

INT. WARM KITCHEN - MORNING

A baker's hands lift a golden, crusty sourdough loaf out of an oven. Steam rises. The loaf glows.

CUT TO:

INT. WARM KITCHEN - MORNING

Wide still-life on a marble counter: a sliced sourdough loaf on a wooden board, butter melting on a slice, the Empire Red Artisan stand mixer at quiet attention beside it.

FADE OUT.
